@startuml child_lock_and_access_auth_to_door_rr_unlock_gate_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Child Lock And Access Auth To Door RR Unlock Gate Signal Flow\n(door control + child-lock + access authorization -> DOOR_RR unlock gate)

participant "Door-control bus" as DoorCtl #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "Digital-key /\nimmobilizer buses" as Access #FCE8FF
participant "DOOR_RR\nrear-right door owner" as DoorRR #E8F7E8
participant "Door RR state bus" as DoorBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nbody readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== Door RR Inputs ==

DoorCtl -> DoorRR : frmDoorControlMsg\nDoorControlCmd / ChildLockCmd
Veh -> DoorRR : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
Access -> DoorRR : frmDigitalKeyStateMsg\nVehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
Access -> DoorRR : frmImmobilizerStateMsg\nImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
activate DoorRR
DoorRR -> DoorRR : freshness checks for\ndoor control, vehicle, dkey, immo
DoorRR -> DoorRR : manualMode allows\nChassis::driveState override
DoorRR -> DoorRR : accessAuthorized =\nvehicle parked and dkey/immo auth valid
DoorRR -> DoorRR : unlockRequest =\ndoor control command > 0
DoorRR -> DoorRR : childLockActive =\nChildLockCmd > 0
DoorRR -> DoorRR : unlock only when\nauthorized and requested and child-lock == 0
note right of DoorRR
Representative gating inputs
- DoorControlCmd
- ChildLockCmd
- gDriveState
- VehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
- ImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
end note

== Door RR Publish ==

DoorRR -> DoorBus : frmDoorRrStateMsg\nDoorRrLockState / DoorRrOpenState / DoorRrWindowPos
note right of DoorRR
Representative outputs
- DoorRrLockState
- DoorRrOpenState
- DoorRrWindowPos
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

DoorBus -> Obs : rear-door lock visibility /\nbody observers
deactivate DoorRR

note over DoorCtl, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Door control, vehicle, digital-key, and immobilizer context reach DOOR_RR
2. DOOR_RR resolves access authorization and child-lock posture
3. Unlock request is gated by park state and child-lock release
4. DOOR_RR publishes final rear-right door lock state
end note

@enduml
